\\begin{itemize}
    \\item $v_i^r$ and $v_j^s$ are in different triples, that is, $r \\neq s$, and
    \\item their corresponding literals are \\textit{consistent}, that is, $l_i^r$ is not the negation of $l_j^s$.
\\end{itemize}
